This directory contains a template for packaging the polls app

Once you have the following files:
- LICENSE
- MANIFEST.in
- README.rst
- setup.cfg
- setup.py
- polls directory with the polls application inside

you can run `python setup.py sdist` to create a tar file under a directory dist

Using the packaged app in another project:

This tar file can then be installed to a virtualenv with `pip install path/to/tar/file`
To make your django project 'aware' of the newly installed app, follow instructions in the README.rst file.